            "title": "Roost selection by male northern long-eared bats (Myotis septentrionalis) in a managed fire-adapted forest",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Jesse M.",
                    "lastName": "Alston"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
