            "title": "Assessing the Structure and Function of Distress Calls in Cuban Fruit-Eating Bats (Brachyphylla nana)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Bryan",
                    "lastName": "Arnold"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
