            "title": "The Potential to Encode Detailed Information About Parasites in the Acoustic Signals of Chinese Horseshoe Bats (Rhinolophus sinicus)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Baozhu",
